
== OUTPUT ==

ATC-pie dumps various log and output files here, possibly overwritten regularly.

For example, when required data is missing for an airfield or no world-wide list
of AD positions is provided, ATC-pie falls back on extracting old data from a
deprecated source and saves it here with a ".extract" extension for quicker
access in later runs.

If you customise extracted files found here, rename/move them where appropriate
to avoid losing your work when this directory is cleared (e.g. on clean-up):
 - see "CONFIG/ad" for individual airport specs (named by ICAO code + ".dat");
 - see "CONFIG/nav" for world locations and names ("AD-positions").

It is safe to delete files here once all sessions are finished, which you can do
with the clean-up script, but the directory itself should not be deleted.

